        "description": "Your company name will be assigned to you or selected by you on day zero of FSY. It serves an important purpose, so incorporate it into your week as much as possible. It will unify your company and help them learn more about their Savior.\nRead your company scripture together, and then tell your youth your company name.\nDiscuss what the company name means to them, using the company scripture to guide the discussion. Ask them how understanding the name will change their week.\n\n• Teach the youth your company chant. This should have been created with your co-CN in the morning on day one. (See instructions under co-counselor planning on page 16.)\n• Explain that this chant will be used throughout the week as your company is released from different activities.",
