        "end": "18:00",
        "description": "PARTICIPANT FLEX TIME\nOn-campus activities take place at this time. Participant flex time provides an opportunity to spend time with your participants and learn more about them.\n\nMUSICAL PROGRAM REHEARSAL\nEncourage your youth to participate in the musical program.\n\nVARIETY SHOW TRYOUTS\nEncourage your youth to try out for the variety show. Review the variety show guidelines (pages 106–07) with them so they understand what is acceptable and appropriate. Remind them to sign up early. Help those not selected for the variety show to understand that the choice isn’t always based on skill or talent, but on need for variety. Consider setting aside time later in the week for those not selected to perform for your company.\n\nON-CAMPUS ACTIVITIES\nOn-campus activities take place during participant flex time.\n\nDINNER AVAILABLE\nDinner is available from 4:30–6:00 p.m.",
